RESTWebSocket (subscribe) <p><code>GET /api/data/values</code></p> <pre><code>[
  {
    "eventType": "TwitchSub",
    "source": "Twitch",
    "meta": "1000",
    "seconds": 60,
    "points": 1
  },
  {
    "eventType": "TwitchSub",
    "source": "Twitch",
    "meta": "2000",
    "seconds": 120,
    "points": 2
  }
]
</code></pre> <p>Send to subscribe - you'll then receive config values any time they update:</p> <pre><code>{ "ws_type": "ValueConfig" }
</code></pre> <p>Response format:</p> <pre><code>{
  "type": "value_config",
  "ws_type": "ValueConfig",
  "data": [
    {
      "eventType": "TwitchSub",
      "source": "Twitch",
      "meta": "1000",
      "seconds": 60,
      "points": 1
    }
  ]
}
</code></pre> <p>Returns all event values that have a points or seconds configuration, along with source and meta data.</p>
